{"about_the_game":"Brought back to the world of the living, you'll need to <strong>survive</strong> as you <strong>explore</strong> stunningly beautiful worlds filled with danger.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/DescrIMG.png?t=1722800546\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is Lendas?</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/lendassmall.png?t=1722800546\" />is a <strong>Survival</strong> and <strong>Exploration</strong> game with <strong>Action RPG</strong> elements. It takes place in <strong>procedurally generated worlds</strong> with <strong>living ecosystems</strong>. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/jumpfly.gif?t=1722800546\" /><br>Face creatures inspired by the <strong>Brazilian folklore</strong> and <strong>steal their powers</strong> to bring you one step closer to your revenge.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/Boitata.gif?t=1722800546\" /><br><br>You will need to <strong>harvest</strong> resources, <strong>build items</strong>, <strong>hunt</strong> powerful creatures and <strong>build shelters</strong> that will help you survive.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/Lob.gif?t=1722800546\" /><br><br><strong>Lendas</strong> has an advanced survival system, which features gathering and crafting items, a day and night system, and a hunger and thirst system.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749400/extras/dayandnight.gif?t=1722800546\" /><br><br>The <strong>character creation</strong> system is quite detailed. Players can change from eye distance to upper lip size.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.